name: MARIA CHILI KEITH OTTER / MARIACHI LIKE IT HOTTER
description: Is word spacing really that important? Does it matter? Apparently it does because if we just move 4 small spaces in this top list over, the next line says something completely and utterly different. Granted, these  lines are absolute nonsense, but it illustrates a hyperbole of the possibilities within the English language. I mean who knew that Mariachi like it hotter? I didn't, but now I know.
